        <headline>Severe Thunderstorm Warning issued April 22 at 4:26PM CDT until April 22 at 5:00PM CDT by NWS Midland/Odessa TX</headline>
        <description>At 425 PM CDT, a severe thunderstorm was located 6 miles north of
Fort Stockton, and is nearly stationary.

HAZARD...Two inch hail and 70 mph wind gusts.

SOURCE...Trained weather spotters.

IMPACT...People and animals outdoors will be injured. Expect hail
damage to roofs, siding, windows, and vehicles. Expect
considerable tree damage. Wind damage is also likely to
mobile homes, roofs, and outbuildings.

Locations impacted include...
Imperial.
</description>
        <instruction>For your protection move to an interior room on the lowest floor of a
building.</instruction>
